[
  {
    "startTime": 0.0,
    "endTime": 2.2,
    "text": "I saw a photo of you from your high school."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 2.2,
    "endTime": 3.34,
    "text": "Where did you go to high school?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 3.34,
    "endTime": 5.58,
    "text": "I went to high school in Oxon Hill, Maryland."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 5.58,
    "endTime": 7.38,
    "text": "Oxon Hill High School."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 7.38,
    "endTime": 11.92,
    "text": "Okay, and normally, high school photos are pretty lame."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11.92,
    "endTime": 12.92,
    "text": "They can be."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 12.92,
    "endTime": 15.620000000000001,
    "text": "Mine was terrible. I grew a mustache."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17.0,
    "endTime": 18.559,
    "text": "I started a mustache. It was really, like..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.559,
    "endTime": 20.059,
    "text": "I have a feeling you're going to show my picture."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 20.059,
    "endTime": 22.12,
    "text": "I think it's only fair you show yours, too."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 22.12,
    "endTime": 23.559,
    "text": "Oh, I don't have mine, sorry."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.559,
    "endTime": 25.5,
    "text": "But I do have yours."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.5,
    "endTime": 26.2,
    "text": "I'm sure you do."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26.2,
    "endTime": 28.4,
    "text": "But look at this. You're a babe."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.0,
    "endTime": 32.86,
    "text": "I love you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.86,
    "endTime": 34.799,
    "text": "Look at the style."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.799,
    "endTime": 37.599,
    "text": "Look at the style. Look at that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 37.599,
    "endTime": 39.48,
    "text": "Look at the style."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.48,
    "endTime": 40.98,
    "text": "Look at that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.98,
    "endTime": 44.778999999999996,
    "text": "Come on. I mean, that's a professional picture right there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.779,
    "endTime": 46.279,
    "text": "Actually, it is."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.279,
    "endTime": 47.279,
    "text": "It is, right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.279,
    "endTime": 50.619,
    "text": "Yeah, because I didn't like the photographer they were using for the, um..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53.0,
    "endTime": 53.66,
    "text": "In high school?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53.66,
    "endTime": 55.019999999999996,
    "text": "In high school. I didn't like it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55.02,
    "endTime": 57.2,
    "text": "I just saw the pictures. I was like, eh, boring."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.299,
    "endTime": 59.0,
    "text": "So I wanted to shake it up a bit."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 59.0,
    "endTime": 62.86,
    "text": "So I went and found my own photographer."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.86,
    "endTime": 63.3,
    "text": "Really?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 63.3,
    "endTime": 64.2,
    "text": "I did."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.2,
    "endTime": 67.839,
    "text": "You look fantastic. What a good style. - I took my wardrobe and all my different changes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67.839,
    "endTime": 72.9,
    "text": "Yeah, I mean, you had the glasses matching the top with the shoulder pads."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.9,
    "endTime": 74.98,
    "text": "The dolphin door knockers."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 74.98,
    "endTime": 78.48,
    "text": "I had my name, the correct spelling of my name, in case you didn't, you know..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 78.48,
    "endTime": 79.879,
    "text": "Yeah, of course, yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.879,
    "endTime": 82.68,
    "text": "Taraji wasn't the very... It wasn't the easiest name, you know."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 82.68,
    "endTime": 85.30000000000001,
    "text": "No, it's not the easiest name, but you had style back then."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.3,
    "endTime": 86.419,
    "text": "Thank you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.48,
    "endTime": 88.48,
    "text": "Congrats on Empire now. Season four?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.48,
    "endTime": 92.0,
    "text": "Yes. - Already?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 92.0,
    "endTime": 93.3,
    "text": "I can't believe it's four seasons already."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.3,
    "endTime": 94.48,
    "text": "Time flies."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 94.48,
    "endTime": 95.2,
    "text": "How's Terrence doing?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.2,
    "endTime": 97.48,
    "text": "You got to tell him I said hi. - He's good. I will, I will."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.48,
    "endTime": 98.10000000000001,
    "text": "He's doing good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 98.1,
    "endTime": 99.19999999999999,
    "text": "What's happening this season?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 99.2,
    "endTime": 100.10000000000001,
    "text": "What do we got to know?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.1,
    "endTime": 100.1,
    "text": "Oh, my goodness."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.5,
    "endTime": 102.699,
    "text": "So, Terrence can't remember anything."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.699,
    "endTime": 105.0,
    "text": "Well, Lucius, he can't remember anything."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 105.0,
    "endTime": 106.16,
    "text": "From the explosion."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.16,
    "endTime": 107.16,
    "text": "From the explosion."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 107.16,
    "endTime": 110.16,
    "text": "He's this really nice guy named DeWayne now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 110.16,
    "endTime": 112.16,
    "text": "And Cookie's kind of over it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.16,
    "endTime": 112.89999999999999,
    "text": "She's over it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.9,
    "endTime": 113.80000000000001,
    "text": "She's over it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 113.8,
    "endTime": 116.03999999999999,
    "text": "She wants the roughneck back."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 116.16,
    "endTime": 117.39999999999999,
    "text": "That's what she fell in love with."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.4,
    "endTime": 117.80000000000001,
    "text": "That's right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.8,
    "endTime": 120.8,
    "text": "And now he's all too nice and gushy, kumbaya."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 120.8,
    "endTime": 122.2,
    "text": "She's over it. - No, no, no."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.2,
    "endTime": 124.3,
    "text": "In real life, you're kind of a kumbaya type of..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 124.3,
    "endTime": 125.16,
    "text": "I'm very mushy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 125.16,
    "endTime": 126.7,
    "text": "You are, but you're also..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 126.7,
    "endTime": 128.0,
    "text": "Aren't you very, like, zen?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 128.0,
    "endTime": 128.5,
    "text": "Don't you meditate?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 128.5,
    "endTime": 130.16,
    "text": "I do. I do meditate."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.16,
    "endTime": 131.79999999999998,
    "text": "I'm getting into it. I'm getting into it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 131.8,
    "endTime": 133.4,
    "text": "What's your routine? Can you tell me?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 133.4,
    "endTime": 137.16,
    "text": "Well, the thing is, a lot of people think when you meditate, you have to oom and burn candles."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 137.16,
    "endTime": 139.16,
    "text": "That's one way to do it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 139.16,
    "endTime": 144.16,
    "text": "But a meditative state is just allowing your thoughts to run through until you quiet your mind."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 144.279,
    "endTime": 147.0,
    "text": "You can do that just sitting in a chair looking off into the abyss."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 147.1,
    "endTime": 149.279,
    "text": "Like, you don't have to oom."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 149.4,
    "endTime": 153.8,
    "text": "I think people get overwhelmed when you say meditate because they think it's a whole ritual."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 154.0,
    "endTime": 155.7,
    "text": "It's whatever you make it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 155.7,
    "endTime": 162.39999999999998,
    "text": "So, I literally, I'm in the house, I'll turn the music off, no television, and I'll just move around the house with nothing on."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 162.4,
    "endTime": 163.70000000000002,
    "text": "My thoughts are still running."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 163.7,
    "endTime": 167.1,
    "text": "I just don't try to answer questions or solve the world's problems. - It's a walking meditation?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 167.1,
    "endTime": 167.5,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 167.5,
    "endTime": 168.5,
    "text": "Really?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 168.5,
    "endTime": 173.1,
    "text": "It's a meditative state. You don't have to sit. It's just allowing your brain to calm."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 173.1,
    "endTime": 175.399,
    "text": "Can you communicate with people?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 175.399,
    "endTime": 176.399,
    "text": "No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 176.399,
    "endTime": 179.1,
    "text": "Like, if people go, \"Taraji, hey, yo, are you in a zone?\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 179.1,
    "endTime": 180.29999999999998,
    "text": "You know what? Sometimes in my meditation..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 180.6,
    "endTime": 182.399,
    "text": "Just banging and stuff?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 182.399,
    "endTime": 183.399,
    "text": "No!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 183.399,
    "endTime": 184.399,
    "text": "Is it like sleepwalking?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 184.399,
    "endTime": 185.399,
    "text": "I'm not in a trance."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 185.5,
    "endTime": 186.399,
    "text": "No, Jimmy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 186.399,
    "endTime": 193.399,
    "text": "But what it is is that sometimes I will think about something enough that I will put it in the universe and it will come back to me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 193.399,
    "endTime": 193.8,
    "text": "That has happened a lot."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 193.8,
    "endTime": 195.10000000000002,
    "text": "Really? - Yeah, a lot."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 195.1,
    "endTime": 195.7,
    "text": "I believe that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 195.7,
    "endTime": 199.399,
    "text": "Little things. Little things like, I was thinking about..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 199.399,
    "endTime": 204.0,
    "text": "Oh, I can't tell you. I'm sorry."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 204.0,
    "endTime": 205.3,
    "text": "Cut. Take two."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 205.3,
    "endTime": 207.70000000000002,
    "text": "What was the question?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 207.7,
    "endTime": 210.0,
    "text": "I almost gave him some information."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 212.1,
    "endTime": 215.0,
    "text": "You are so cute. Come on."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 215.0,
    "endTime": 217.0,
    "text": "I love you so much."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 217.0,
    "endTime": 221.8,
    "text": "I love Jimmy and I want to tell him everything but I can't tell you this yet, Jimmy. - Alright, that's cool."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 221.8,
    "endTime": 222.20000000000002,
    "text": "I think I know."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 222.2,
    "endTime": 225.39999999999998,
    "text": "Yeah, I know. Shh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 225.4,
    "endTime": 226.0,
    "text": "What are these things?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 226.0,
    "endTime": 227.8,
    "text": "These are Tibetan singing bowls."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 227.8,
    "endTime": 230.22,
    "text": "Now, this is something that I have to sit down and do."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 230.2,
    "endTime": 234.0,
    "text": "But the vibration of the bowl will put you in a meditative state, because..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 234.2,
    "endTime": 235.7,
    "text": "So your gonna [show] everyone how to meditate?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 235.7,
    "endTime": 238.0,
    "text": "I'm going to show you how to do the Tibetan."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 238.0,
    "endTime": 239.4,
    "text": "You have to do it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 239.4,
    "endTime": 242.6,
    "text": "To watch somebody do it is not the same."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 242.6,
    "endTime": 244.0,
    "text": "No, no, no."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 246.0,
    "endTime": 247.3,
    "text": "Watch first."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 247.3,
    "endTime": 249.0,
    "text": "Dinner's ready, y'all."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 249.0,
    "endTime": 250.0,
    "text": "Come on in. Dinner."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 250.0,
    "endTime": 252.5,
    "text": "We got some grub. We got some grub."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 252.5,
    "endTime": 256.0,
    "text": "Come on in, kids. Come on in, y'all."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 256.0,
    "endTime": 257.4,
    "text": "Wait. I'm doing it wrong? What do you do?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 257.4,
    "endTime": 260.59999999999997,
    "text": "Well, you could.... that's one way to do it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 260.6,
    "endTime": 261.1,
    "text": "But..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 261.1,
    "endTime": 262.90000000000003,
    "text": "That really gets me really zenned out."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 262.9,
    "endTime": 263.76,
    "text": "I'm really..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 266.5,
    "endTime": 269.0,
    "text": "It's too relaxed."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 269.0,
    "endTime": 269.6,
    "text": "Patience."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 269.6,
    "endTime": 273.0,
    "text": "Sorry, sorry, sorry, sorry."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 278.0,
    "endTime": 279.0,
    "text": "Can you hear it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 279.0,
    "endTime": 280.0,
    "text": "Is that real?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 280.0,
    "endTime": 281.0,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 281.0,
    "endTime": 282.0,
    "text": "Is that coming from that?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 282.0,
    "endTime": 284.0,
    "text": "Yes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 284.0,
    "endTime": 287.6,
    "text": "Are you kidding me?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 287.6,
    "endTime": 290.279,
    "text": "It is coming from that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 290.279,
    "endTime": 292.7,
    "text": "I thought that was James playing the keyboard or something."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 292.7,
    "endTime": 293.59999999999997,
    "text": "That was weird."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 293.6,
    "endTime": 296.3,
    "text": "Dude, that just freaked me out, man."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 296.3,
    "endTime": 296.90000000000003,
    "text": "That freaked me out."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 296.9,
    "endTime": 298.0,
    "text": "How do you do that? - Try it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 298.0,
    "endTime": 299.3,
    "text": "You have to be very..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 299.3,
    "endTime": 300.2,
    "text": "It teaches you...."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 300.2,
    "endTime": 301.459,
    "text": "You have to hold it, Jimmy. You have to hold it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 306.7,
    "endTime": 307.5,
    "text": "Do you feel it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 307.5,
    "endTime": 310.5,
    "text": "You're going too fast, Jimmy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 310.5,
    "endTime": 312.079,
    "text": "That's what she said."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 323.119,
    "endTime": 324.76000000000005,
    "text": "I love you, man."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 324.76,
    "endTime": 326.7,
    "text": "Taraji P. Henson, everybody. -  I love you more."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 326.7,
    "endTime": 332.09999999999997,
    "text": "Check out the new season of Empire Wednesday at 8pm on Fox."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 332.1,
    "endTime": 333.1,
    "text": "She's fantastic."
  }
]